Body:
@kclass
class Other:
    n: N(5)
    an: AN(10)
@kclass
class Something:
    n: N(10)
    an: AN(20)
    other: Other
    others: List[Other]
    filler: AN(100)
sth = Something(123, 'k-class', Other(-456, 'subclass'), [], None)
assert sth is not None
sth = Something(n=123, an='k-class', other=Other(-456, 'subclass'), others=
    [], filler=None)
assert sth is not None
one = Other(n=123, an='1')
assert (one.n[1], one.an[1]) == (123, '1')
one = Other(123, an='1')
assert (one.n[1], one.an[1]) == (123, '1')
one = Other(an='1', n=123)
assert (one.n[1], one.an[1]) == (123, '1')
